<p>So Jodie Turner-Smith was the perfect model to pose in Kim Kardashian's shapewear line SKIMS on Thursday. </p>

<p>The 33-year-old Queen &amp; Slim actress looked radiant in a white tank bodysuit for the photoshoot, which she shared to her Instagram. </p>

