<p>An accompanying video showed the model and actress unpacking a vintage suitcase while rocking the shapewear.</p>

<p>Turner-Smith captioned the post, 'happy birthday <?php echo e('@'); ?>skims! really excited to be a part of the 1 Year Anniversary campaign because my body has changed so much in the last year and at every size i’ve felt sexy in <?php echo e('@'); ?>skims'.</p>

<p>The English beauty concluded her post, 'thank you for supporting me from press tour to postpartum'.  </p>

